responseElements.x-amz-id-2: Amazon S3 host that processed the request

s3.configurationId: ID found in the bucket notification configuration

object.versionId: object version if bucket is versioning-enabled, otherwise null
object.sequencer: a string representation of a hexadecimal value used to determine event sequence, only used with PUTs and DELETEs

restoreEventData.lifecycleRestorationExpiryTime: The time, in ISO-8601 format, for example, 1970-01-01T00:00:00.000Z, of Restore Expiry
